---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy | Bluebird"
	description="How Bluebird handles personal information and contact form submissions."
	canonicalURL="/privacy"
>
	<section class="relative pt-28 sm:pt-32 md:pt-36 pb-16 sm:pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-bg overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-accent/3 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-accentSubtle/30 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow-delay"></div>

		<div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text leading-tight mb-4">
				Privacy Policy
			</h1>
			<p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-textMuted leading-relaxed mb-10">
				We respect your privacy. This page explains what information we collect and how we use it.
			</p>

			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/50 p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">What we collect</h2>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
						<li>- Information you submit through our contact form (such as your name, email, and message).</li>
						<li>- Basic, anonymous usage data that may be collected by your browser or hosting provider (for example, server logs).</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/50 p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">How we use your information</h2>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
						We use the information you provide only to respond to your inquiry, discuss your project, and provide support related to your request.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/50 p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Data storage</h2>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
						We don’t sell your data and we don’t store personal information beyond what you voluntarily submit to contact us. We keep contact form
						messages only as long as needed to communicate with you and maintain normal business records.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/50 p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
						This website may rely on third-party infrastructure (such as hosting, email, or analytics). Those providers may process limited data to
						deliver their services. We only use reputable providers and keep access limited.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-accentSubtle/50 p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
					<p class="text-sm text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
						If you have questions about privacy, email us at
						<a href="mailto:info@bluebirdweb.ca" class="text-accent hover:text-accentDark transition-colors">info@bluebirdweb.ca</a>.
					</p>
				</div>

				<p class="text-xs text-textMuted">
					Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-CA', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
	@keyframes pulseSlow {
		0%,
		100% {
			opacity: 0.3;
			transform: scale(1);
		}
		50% {
			opacity: 0.5;
			transform: scale(1.1);
		}
	}

	.animate-pulse-slow {
		animation: pulseSlow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.animate-pulse-slow-delay {
		animation: pulseSlow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
		animation-delay: 2s;
	}
</style>

